{"tid":1174510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為指FedEx將寄往華為中國地址的包裹轉運至美國","createTime":"2019-05-28T01:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T14:21:58.000Z","uid":252013,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"150d55455a3919ab408c97b9033431258a37b910","tid":1174510,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"到底係唔小心定特登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定真係物流需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似睇連續劇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n09:06 據外電引述華為方面指，聯邦快遞將從日本寄往華為中國地址的兩個包裹轉運至美國，並試圖轉運另外兩個由越南寄往華為其他亞洲辦公室的包裹，其行為均未取得華為授權。華為表示正重新審視與聯邦快遞的關係。<br />\n<br />\n華為向外電提供了聯邦快遞包裹追蹤記錄的圖片，但...<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=892a1ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a>"},{"pid":"879bf2a4eab7befb4f1d8c01715d2528b06062b1","tid":1174510,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c659870a502c4e0eb6140dfbc4a2cca9e11461","tid":1174510,"uid":246419,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:10:36.000Z","msg":"又要用又要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb61f558f79ad026d11ae78eeeb05c4879a83fb2","tid":1174510,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"轉運/失誤姐"},{"pid":"cc8dd3e1afc